race.description: Jgp We Stand With Tassie Pathways F
race.comment: RICKY BOBBY (3) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 20.29 beating RACING QUEEN. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Great chance to get the job done again. HOOKED ON MAGIC (1) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only one length from BLACK RASPBERRY in second (20.43) at this track. Expecting another good run. INFRARED POWER (2) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 20.20 beating CASH PROMISED. Can measure up again. CASH PROMISED (6) was in the money last start as favourite - poses a threat again.
